@startuml seq-06-like
' 序列图6：点赞文章
title 点赞文章序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "article-detail.js" as Front
participant "ArticleController" as Ctrl
participant "LikeService" as Svc
participant "LikeMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 点击点赞按钮
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/article/{id}/like
Ctrl -> Svc: toggleLike(userId,target_type=1,target_id)
Svc -> Mapper: select(userId,target_type,target_id)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM like_record WHERE...
DB --> Mapper: 记录(无)
Mapper --> Svc: null
Svc -> Mapper: insert(userId,target_type,target_id)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO like_record
Svc -> Mapper: updateArticleLikeCount(id,+1)
Mapper -> DB: UPDATE article SET like_count=like_count+1
Svc --> Ctrl: 已点赞
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, liked:true}
Front -> Front: 更新点赞数+1,按钮变色
Front --> User: 显示已点赞状态

@enduml
